text: Not sure what the rest of the reviews are saying, but the DBS ATM is still functional and it's there at the basement. It's right by Ya Kun Kaya Toast, so if you're coming down the escalator right by Starbucks, turn left and walk towards Din Tai Fung, you should be able to find it before you hit the Ramen restaurant.
DBS ATM has been relocated to B2 near the Sancho Taqueria escalator.
